.TH "dpm_wait" 9 "dpm_wait" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
dpm_wait \- Wait for a PM operation to complete.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" dpm_wait
.BI "(struct device *dev "  ","
.BI "bool async "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dev" 12
Device to wait for.
.IP "async" 12
If unset, wait only if the device's power.async_suspend flag is set.
